## **8. CI/CD Integration**

### **GitHub Actions Workflow**
```yaml
# .github/workflows/generate-graphics.yml
name: Generate Store Graphics

on:
  push:
    paths:
      - 'assets/graphics/feature-graphic/source/**'

jobs:
  generate:
    runs-on: ubuntu-latest
    steps:
      - uses: actions/checkout@v2
      
      - name: Setup Node.js
        uses: actions/setup-node@v2
        with:
          node-version: '16'
      
      - name: Install dependencies
        run: npm install canvas sharp
      
      - name: Generate feature graphic
        run: node generate-feature-graphic.js
      
      - name: Optimize images
        run: node optimize-graphics.js
      
      - name: Validate output
        run: node validate-graphics.js
      
      - name: Commit generated files
        run: |
          git config --local user.email "action@github.com"
          git config --local user.name "GitHub Action"
          git add assets/graphics/Feature_Graphic.png
          git commit -m "Auto-generate feature graphic" || echo "No changes"
          git push
```

